description:
Rapper, Saweetie, speaks on a range of topics including why her Maxim photo shoot was historic, she opens up about her alter ego "Professor Icy,” her love live in the bed with Quavo, and much more! Guest host Chaunte Wayans gets graphic about her favorite positions and even shoots her shot at Saweetie! Enjoy!
